title.text: Adventure is calling louder than ever. The versatile BMW X1 models deliver all-terrain performance, power, and efficiency in a rugged utility vehicle.

title.name: highlights
title.description: The versatile BMW X1 Sports Activity Vehicle®  packs a lot of power and personality in a compact body – including these features, new for 2023.

description.title: Fingertip control.
description.text: The expansive BMW Curved Display, appearing on the X1 for the first time, includes touch-focused interaction design.

description.title: Bold and bright.
description.text: Discover the biggest range of exterior paint finishes ever available for the X1 – and the stylish upgrades of the xLine Package.

description.title: Supportive seats.
description.text: Add the available Sport Seats with SensaTec upholstery for a new level of driving comfort and support.

title.name: performance
title.description: Power in a small package. With exceptional engineering, a wider stance, and available design enhancements, the BMW X1 SAV delivers outsized performance.

description.title: Strong hearted.
description.text: A 2.0-liter BMW TwinPower Turbo inline 4-cylinder engine drives the new BMW X1, turning out 241 horsepower. Shift smoothly with the automatic 7-speed Dual Clutch Transmission.

description.title: All-condition control.
description.text: The BMW X1 xDrive28i includes BMW's powerful and intelligent all-wheel drive system as standard. When slip due to rain, snow, or loose surfaces is detected, xDrive automatically distributes power between the wheels for better control in adverse conditions.

description.title: Broader body.
description.text: A wider front and rear stance improves the dynamics and handling of the all-new BMW X1 – demonstrating the "sport" in Sports Activity Vehicle.

description.title: Take sportiness to the top.
description.text: The available M Sport Package ups the style and handling of your 2023 BMW X1 with additional wheel designs, the Adaptive M Suspension, M steering wheel with paddle shifters, and many other enhancements.

title.text: Adventure is calling louder than ever. The versatile BMW X3 models deliver all-terrain performance, power, and efficiency in a rugged utility vehicle.

title.name: highlights
title.description: The 12.3" Central Information Display is an ideal portal for the intuitive iDrive 7 Operating System and its customizable information and entertainment.

description.title: Take control.
description.text: A Panoramic Moonroof – standard on the X3 M40i, and available for other models – opens up the cabin interior while providing an amazing view.

description.title: Open sky feeling.
description.text: Discover the biggest range of exterior paint finishes ever available for the X1 – and the stylish upgrades of the xLine Package.

description.title: Sporty seating.
description.text: Standard Sport Seats can be equipped with perforated SensaTec upholstery – a luxurious and durable surface that's ready for anything.

title.name: performance
title.description: From luxurious and comfortable utility vehicles to precision-engineered high-performance machines, the 2023 BMW X3 lineup delivers the power you need for your next adventure.

description.title: Engines for everything.
description.text: BMW TwinPower Turbo engines are crafted for reliability and power output, from the 2.0-liter inline 4-cylinder of the sDrive30i and xDrive30i models, to the 382-hp M TwinPower Turbo engine in the X3 M40i.

description.title: Automatic as standard.
description.text: Every BMW X3 model includes the 8-speed Sport Automatic Transmission as standard, for smooth-shifting precision no matter how you drive.

description.title: Power personified.
description.text: Performance-minded drivers will love the BMW X3 M40i, engineered by BMW M. Enhanced engines, superior handing, and model-specific design make this a standout SAV.

title.text: The curves of a coupe and the power of an athlete – the BMW X4 stands apart in style and performance.

title.name: highlights
title.description: Modern style meets modern comforts. The 2023 X4 features large displays, invigorating colors, and plush seating.

description.title: Driver-focused display.
description.text: You’re at the center of it all. The X4’s modern interior features the standard 12.3” Central Information Display.

description.title: Show your true colors.
description.text: Set your X4 apart with dynamic color options – including Brooklyn Grey, Piemont Red, Aventurin Red, and Tanzanite Blue.

description.title: Comfortable seats.
description.text: Luxurious SensaTec upholstery, available in striking Tacora Red and Cognac colors, enhances the standard Sport Seats even further.

title.name: performance
title.description: From luxurious and comfortable utility vehicles to precision-engineered high-performance machines, the 2023 BMW X4 lineup delivers the power you need for your next adventure.

description.title: POWER AT PLAY
description.text: The X4 exhibits the strength and speed of an athlete with BMW TwinPower Turbo engines – an inline 4-cylinder engine in the X4 xDrive30i and an inline 6-cylinder engine in the M40i. Plus, for quick and precise shifts, the X4 boasts a standard 8-Speed Sport Automatic Transmission.

title.text: With its advanced engineering and impressive design, the BMW X5 gets you where you need to be.

title.name: highlights
title.description: Efficient power, brighter light intensity, and polished details – the X5 shines on every level.

description.title: Power meets efficiency.
description.text: With 48V mild-hybrid technology, the inline 6-cylinder engine in the X5 sDrive40i and xDrive40i delivers heightened eBoost power and optimal efficiency.

description.title: Striking headlight design.
description.text: Available Icon LED Headlights provide intuitive technology that adjusts to road conditions, and a smart aesthetic – which can be enhanced even further with available blue design accents.

description.title: Available Glass Controls.
description.text: Every detail in the X5 is honed to perfection. Available Glass Controls add an ultra-modern touch to features like your gear selector, start button, and iDrive Controller.

title.name: performance
title.description: Vacation rides, long drives, and everyday lives. Whether you’re seeking out thrills or convenience, the 2023 BMW X5 midsize SAV is ready to perform.

description.title: Power-packed engines.
description.text: There’s a lot of power under the hood of a BMW X5, whether you choose the inline-6 with 48V mild-hybrid technology, a fuel-efficient plug-in hybrid powertrain, or the M-tuned V-8 engine of the BMW X5 M50i.

description.title: Advanced handling.
description.text: With standard Dynamic Damper Control and your choice of Adaptive M Suspension or 2-axle air suspension, the BMW X5 is ready for the toughest challenges.

description.title: Impressive presence.
description.text: The BMW X5 delivers confidence in its very appearance. An active kidney grille and side air breathers improve the aerodynamics and emphasize the sportiness of this midsize Sports Activity Vehicle.

description.title: Power and versatility.
description.text: Command every road with the BMW M engineering on the X5 M50i. Standard Adaptive M Suspension, M Sport Brakes, M Differential, and the powerful BMW M engine can you take you farther than you’ve ever been before.

title.text: An athletic, powerful BMW that leads with standout design and impressive performance.

title.name: highlights
title.description: Transformative design. Convenient features. Connected technology. The 2023 BMW X6 Sports Activity Coupe was designed to fit perfectly into your life.

description.title: Dominating design.
description.text: An available M Sport Package enhances the X6 xDrive40i with the Aerodynamic Kit, M Sport suspension, and additional wheel options.

description.title: Seamless compatibility.
description.text: Standard wireless Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto™ compatibility keeps you up to date and connected to all your favorite apps and mobile content.

description.title: Expansive views.
description.text: Bring the outside in with the standard Panoramic Moonroof, which floods your cabin with fresh air and natural light.

title.name: performance
title.description: The X6 Sports Activity Coupe puts you in a position of power with BMW TwinPower Turbo engines – an inline 6-cylinder enhanced with the latest 48V mild hybrid technology in the X6 xDrive40i and a V-8 engine in the M50i with standard M Sport Exhaust System. Plus, the X6 also boasts a standard 8-speed Sport Automatic Transmission for precise shifting.

description.title: Precise athleticism.
description.text: Every X6 includes standard xDrive, BMW’s intelligent all-wheel drive system, which automatically distributes power between wheels for optimal traction and control. Adaptive M Suspension, standard on the M50i and available on the xDrive40i, allows you to choose between a more relaxed or sporty drive – while M Sport Brakes are always ready for action with a precise response and a standout look.

title.name: WHAT'S NEW
title.description: The sports sedan that started it all continues its exciting evolution with bold styling, modern finishes, and intuitive technology.

description.title: A bold hello.
description.text: The reshaped kidney grille and slim LED headlight design make a strong first impression.

description.title: Ahead of the curve.
description.text: The all-new BMW Curved Display – combining a 12.3" Digital Instrument Cluster and 14.9" Central Information Display – makes interacting with the latest iDrive 8 Operating System easy.

description.title: Shifting style.
description.text: A brand-new rocker switch for gear selection adds seductive style and function to the central console.

title.name: performance
title.description: The original 3 Series Sedan brought power, agility, and spirit to the everyday driver. With efficient technology and refined engineering, that performance has only grown more pronounced.

description.title: The power for more.
description.text: The 3 Series brings power and innovation together in a sedan made to move – from the combustion engine and integrated electric motor of the 330e to the M340i’s robust inline-6 that can generate up to 382 horsepower.

description.title: Class-defining handling.
description.text: With a low center of gravity, lightweight components, and a suspension tuned to perfection on the grueling Nürburgring, this compact sedan delivers incredible sportiness and dynamics.

description.title: The feel of performance.
description.text: With M-engineered components including brakes, suspension, and a 3.0-liter inline-6 cylinder BMW M TwinPower Turbo engine augmented with 48V mild hybrid technology, the M340i models bring aggressive performance to the sports sedan lineup.
